# agent-kit agent command sample list
#
# One command name per line. Empty lines and comments are ignored.
# On first install, install-auto-bootstrap can initialize a real agents list
# from this sample and keep only commands currently found on PATH.
#
# To enable an optional command permanently, copy this file to your real
# agents list and uncomment the entry.

codex
claude
gemini

